Following this first route I received the suggestion to think about creatures and their genetics, on how the change of one character in a creature determines its success over others. \
So I started thinking about a game that would allow some kind of "battling", and after each battle one character would be changed on the victor and then rebattled with its previous self. at the end of which a winner creature would emerge.\
\
Then thinking more about the mechanics of the game I realized that it would have not been extremely exciting and could have been quite boring.\
