\i \ul The Final Project
\i0 \ulnone \
So after some more brainstorming I decided to make my application evolve to an evolutionary ecosystem.\
I set to have 3 links in the food chain, 3 creatures. The first one, an armless source of food, and fundamental base of the ecosystem. The second link, a medium creature feeding on the first one, and which is prey to the third creature, the bigger predator, which existence is based only on the food that can find.\
The environment then can change and affects:\
- the speed of the movement\
- the cratures' reproduction rate\
The user, can then modify and tweak characteristics of the the second and third creature to have them adapt to the environment.\
\
The result is an interesting scene were is possible to see an emergent behavior of creatures feeding and living and understand how the equilibrium of an ecosystem is incredibly fragile.\
